## Minimal page.tsx (copy exactly)

```tsx
import type { Metadata } from 'next'
import { ContentPageTemplate } from '@/components/content/ContentPageTemplate'
import { loadContent } from '@/lib/specs/loader'

const content = loadContent('your-slug')

export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: content.meta.title,
  description: content.meta.description,
}

export default function Page() {
  return <ContentPageTemplate content={content} compact />
}
```

## New page checklist

1. Copy JSON from `titulos-nossa-senhora-template.json` or `ministerios-template.json`
2. Copy `app/titulos-nossa-senhora/template/page.tsx` (or ministerios equivalent)
3. Register slug in `lib/specs/types.ts` + `lib/specs/loader.ts`
4. Add route in `specs/routes.json` with `parent`
5. Add listing card in `titulos-nossa-senhora.json` or `ministerios.json`
6. Add redirect in `vercel.json` if renaming legacy URLs
7. Run `npm run test:specs` and `npm run test:e2e`
